"{\"uid\": \"enca.com-opinion-paris-olympics-set-gold-medal-luxury-promotion\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS - From the podium to athletes' wardrobes, French luxury goods giant LVMH is planning to put high-end Gallic chic at the heart of the Paris Olympics, underlining how sport has become a promotional platform for even the most exclusive brands.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9478223199581224, \"rank\": 0.054499376025839465, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 78, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531347837895293e-67, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 13, \"to\": 23}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' wardrobes\", \"from\": 27, \"to\": 46}, {\"ngram\": \"high-end Gallic chic\", \"from\": 98, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 131}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 153}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 176}, {\"ngram\": \"a promotional platform\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 210}, {\"ngram\": \"even the most exclusive brands\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisian luxury jewellery house Chaumet, one of LVMH's lesser-known properties, was thrust into the public limelight on Thursday when its design for the medals for the July 26-August 11 extravaganza was unveiled.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531347837895293e-67, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisian luxury jewellery house Chaumet\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"the public limelight\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"its design\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"-August\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The role was a departure from its usual niche making engagement rings, tiaras and diamond-studded broaches for the ultra-wealthy, with LVMH hoping to harness the huge international reach of the Olympics on home turf.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The role\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"a departure\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"its usual niche making engagement rings\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"tiaras\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"diamond-studded broaches\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"LVMH\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge international reach\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"home turf\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Antoine Arnault, senior LVMH executive and eldest son of company founder Bernard Arnault, said at the ceremony to reveal the medals that there was a \\\"quasi-military organisation inside the company\\\" working on Paris Olympics projects.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Arnault\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antoine Arnault\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Arnault\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Arnault\"}, {\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531347837895293e-67, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}, {\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Arnault\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bernard Arnault\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Arnault\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Arnault\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eldest son\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"quasi-military organisation\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"LVMH as a partner will try to add a little touch of creativity, notably during the moments of celebration,\\\" he told reporters.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LVMH\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"a partner\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"a little touch\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the moments\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"celebration\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Controlled by the world's richest man, Bernard Arnault, LVMH signed up as \\\"premium partner\\\" for the Paris Games in July last year after months of complex negotiations about the use of its brands.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Arnault\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bernard Arnault\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Arnault\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Arnault\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531347837895293e-67, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's richest man\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"premium partner\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"complex negotiations\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"its brands\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Chaumet secured the medal honour, high-end leather goods brand Berluti is set to dress the French athletes during the spectacular opening ceremony being planned on the river Seine on July 26.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berluti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Berluti\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berluti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berluti\"}, {\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9478223199581224, \"rank\": 0.054499376025839465, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chaumet\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal honour\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectacular opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thousands of Olympics VIPs and high-paying corporate guests are set to sip LVMH-owned Moet & Chandon champagne as well as Hennessy cognac among other premium drinks in their hospitality suites.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mo\\u00ebt_&_Chandon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moet & Chandon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q156362\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mo\\u00ebt_&_Chandon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mo\\u00ebt_&_Chandon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thousands\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"VIPs\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"high-paying corporate guests\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"Hennessy cognac\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"other premium drinks\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"their hospitality suites\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dior is also set for a role -- which has not yet been announced -- as is celebrated handbag and luggage maker Louis Vuitton.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dior\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A series of LVMH-sponsored sports ambassadors will help promote the brand on social media, with 21-year-old French swimming medal hope Leon Marchand one of the earliest names revealed.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9478223199581224, \"rank\": 0.054499376025839465, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A series\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"LVMH-sponsored sports ambassadors\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"the earliest names\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Luxurious sports - LVMH has declined to make public how much it is contributing to the 4.4-billion-euro ($4.7 billion) organising budget of the Games.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1969, \"end\": 1973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531347837895293e-67, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 4.4-billion-euro ($4.7 billion) organising budget\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A source close to the negotiations told AFP at the time that it was worth around 150 million euros ($160 million) -- around one percent of the record 15.2 billion euros in net profit posted by the group last year.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999982924679015, \"rank\": 1.7075150330226772e-06, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A source\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the negotiations\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"around one percent\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"the record 15.2 billion euros\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"net profit\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Commenting on why LVMH took so long negotiating its deal with the Paris organisation, Antoine Arnault explained in July that the company \\\"did not want to just be a financial partner.\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2335, \"end\": 2339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531347837895293e-67, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}, {\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.875469999004644e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2403, \"end\": 2418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Arnault\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antoine Arnault\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Arnault\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Arnault\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its deal\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"a financial partner\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to have a role to play in the holding of these Olympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"the holding\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2547}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LVMH is the world's biggest luxury goods giant, with brands across fashion, jewellery, perfume, alcohol and luggage that trade on France's centuries-old reputation as a centre of taste-making and artistry.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2650, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.66895975750043e-23, \"text\": \"jewellery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\"}, {\"begin\": 2704, \"end\": 2710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999969132835584, \"rank\": 3.0867938445884635e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LVMH\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest luxury goods giant\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"perfume\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2677}, {\"ngram\": \"luggage\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"a centre\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"taste-making\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2765}, {\"ngram\": \"artistry\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"France and Paris are such a potent association for luxury brands, it's kind of a no-brainer for LVMH to want to be as involved as they can be,\\\" said Robert Williams, luxury editor at The Business of Fashion, a specialist fashion publisher.\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999969132835584, \"rank\": 3.0867938445884635e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.875469999004644e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2878, \"end\": 2882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531347837895293e-67, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a potent association\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"luxury brands\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of a no-brainer\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"Robert Williams\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"luxury editor\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"The Business\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"Fashion\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"a specialist fashion publisher\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports were \\\"a space where brands have been ramping up significantly in recent years\\\".\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from